Package: qsimulatR
Version: 0.1
Date: 2020-05-05
Title: A quantum computer simulator in R
Authors@R: 
    c(person(given = "Johann",
             family = "Ostmeyer",
             role = "aut",
             email = "ostmeyer@hiskp.uni-bonn.de"),
      person(given = "Carsten",
             family = "Urbach",
             role = c("aut", "cre"),
             email = "urbach@hiskp.uni-bonn.de"))
Description: A quantum computer simulator framework. It currently implements the
    most common gates (X, Y, Z, H, Z, S, T, Rz, CNOT), supports plotting
    of circuits and is able to export circuits into IBM's QASM python 
    language.
Imports:
    methods,
    stats
Suggests:
    knitr
